sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Inst as Institution
    participant FE as React SPA
    participant API as Express API
    participant Hash as hash.service
    participant QR as qr/pdf.service
    participant IPFS as IPFS / Pinata
    participant BC as Blockchain
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Inst->>FE: Select student + upload PDF
    FE->>API: POST /api/transcripts/issue (multipart, JWT)
    API->>API: Authorize (role=institution, owns student)
    API->>QR: Generate QR for /verify/{transcriptId}
    API->>QR: Stamp QR onto PDF (last page)
    API->>Hash: SHA-256 of stamped PDF
    API->>IPFS: uploadFile(stampedPDF)
    IPFS-->>API: { cid, url }
    API->>BC: addTranscript(transcriptId, studentId, cid, sha256)
    BC-->>API: { txHash, blockNumber }
    API->>DB: Save Transcript document
    API-->>FE: 201 { transcript, qr, verifyUrl, downloadUrl }
    FE-->>Inst: Success card (QR + on-chain proof)
